doxygen-awesome-css v2.4.2
https://github.com/jothepro/doxygen-awesome-css
Upstream commit: 82d315e (MIT, see LICENSE in this directory)

Vendored selectively: only the files the Doxyfile loads are kept, so the darkmode-toggle
extension is not among them (dark mode is pinned in doxygen-header.html, so a toggle would
have nothing to toggle).

doxygen-awesome-sidebar-only.css is loaded, but it was written when Doxygen emitted the
sidebar head and the tree as siblings, and 1.16 nests the head inside the sidebar. The
correction is in doxygen-synqt.css rather than here, so this directory stays a verbatim
copy of upstream and can be replaced wholesale on the next release.
